vehicles]]\n[[Category:Sedans]]\n[[Category:Taxicab vehicles]]\n[[Category:Volkswagen Beetle]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Car model}}\n{{About|the original Volkswagen Beetle|the 1997\u20132010 car|Volkswagen New Beetle|the 2011\u20132019 car|Volkswagen Beetle (A5)}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=June 2011}}\n{{Infobox automobile\n| name = Volkswagen Beetle Type 1\n| image = VW 1302 (2013-09-15 2307 Spu).JPG\n| caption = 1971\u20131973 Volkswagen Type 1 1302\n| manufacturer = [[Volkswagen]]\n| aka = {{plainlist|\n*\"Beetle\"<ref name=samba-1970-ca-full>{{cite web| year =1970 | location = Canada | title = Full line | type = brochure|url= http://www.thesamba.com/vw/archives/lit/70cdnfullline.php | work = The samba | accessdate = 1 June 2011}}</ref>/\"Super Beetle\"<ref name= samba-1970-us-super>{{cite web| year = 1971 | location = US | title = Super Beetle Sedan and Convertible | type = sales brochure |url=http://www.thesamba.com/vw/archives/lit/71superbeetle.php|work=The samba | accessdate = 1 June 2011}}</ref>\n*\"Bug\" / \"Superbug\"<ref>[http://www.clubvw.org.au/austvw001 \"Australian Volkswagens\", www.clubvw.org.au] Retrieved on 26 February 2014</ref>\n*\"{{lang|de|italics=no|K\u00e4fer}}\"<ref name=samba-1973-de-super>{{cite web| year =1973 | title = Super Beetle | type = brochure |url= http://www.thesamba.com/vw/archives/lit/1303.php |work=The Samba |language=German |accessdate=3 June 2011}}</ref>\n*VW 1200, 1300, 1500, 1302/1303,<ref>[https://www.thesamba.com/vw/archives/lit/1971bug_1302_danish.php www.thesamba.com] Retrieved 5 January 2017</ref> \"Garbus\"}}/[[Fusca]]/[[Carocha]]\n| assembly = {{plainlist|\n*Germany: [[Wolfsburg]] (Wolfsburg Volkswagen plant)\n*Germany: [[Hanover]]\n*Germany: [[Emden]]\n*Germany: [[Ingolstadt]]\n*Germany: [[Osnabr\u00fcck]]\n*Australia: [[Melbourne]] ([[Volkswagen Australia|Volkswagen Australia Ltd]]) \n*Belgium: [[Brussels]] ([[Audi Brussels]])\n*Brazil: [[S\u00e3o Bernardo do Campo]]\n*Finland: [[Heinola]]<ref>{{cite web 