gory:Rear-engined vehicles]]\n[[Category:Rear-wheel-drive vehicles]]\n[[Category:Sedans]]\n[[Category:Taxicab vehicles]]\n[[Category:Volkswagen Beetle]]\n", "name_user": "122.171.102.146", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Volkswagen_Beetle"}
